    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836660/extras/b2738f8b0731fdb80ff7c120799d687a.avif?t=1769256352\" width=616 height=346 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>All screenshots are early work-in-progress.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Night Riders</strong> is a modern checkpoint arcade racer series inspired by 1980s retro classics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each season features an exclusive playable female pro racer and 36 stages in 6 locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Night Riders S1</strong> (Season One) is a full remake of the original Super Night Riders (2016) improved on every aspect: Graphics, gameplay, features, balancing and rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play once more as Alice, the beautiful and talented motorcyclist known as the Red Rider, in the 6 original locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836660/extras/f199d17a48b71fcbab47df3e142a87e0.poster.avif?t=1769256352\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836660/extras/f199d17a48b71fcbab47df3e142a87e0.webm?t=1769256352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836660/extras/f199d17a48b71fcbab47df3e142a87e0.mp4?t=1769256352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this series, your position in the race does not matter. It's all about traveling as far as possible while dodging the other riders, and reaching each checkpoint before the timer hits zero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the races starts during the day and continue through the night right up until sunrise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About miyu.works</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >miyu.works is a one cat indie game studio from France making modern renditions of classic concepts.</p>",
